OL,5, The safety of people with learning     
OL,6, disabilities in England is being       
OL,7, compromised when they are admitted to  
OL,8, hospital, a watchdog says.             
OL,10,FThe Health Services Safety             
OL,11,FInvestigations Body (HSSIB) reviewed   
OL,12,Fthe care people receive and said there 
OL,13,Fwere "persistent and widespread" risks.
OL,15,FIt warned staff are not equipped with  
OL,16,Fthe skills or support to meet the needs
OL,17,Fof patients with learning disabilities.
OL,19,FNearly one million adults in England   
OL,20,Fare living with a learning disability. 
